{"tid":1728684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真正令雨革失敗唔單只係快樂抗爭 更多係因為一成不變嘅模式","createTime":"2019-11-17T03:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T08:48:52.000Z","uid":84408,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"26bb2614689ba8efc8462fb9bb0e7dfacc903c9b","tid":1728684,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"唔好睇輕呢加藍絲出黎清rb <br />\n話完全對民意0影響係無可能 <br />\n因為跟本無可能知<br />\n<br />\n民意逆唔逆轉 <br />\n一至兩個月內跟本無可能顯示到出黎 <br />\n更加無可能統計到出黎<br />\n但明顯 對家轉緊策略<br />\n<br />\n而我地呢加嘅文宣策略<br />\n只係流於連濃牆同埋連登<br />\n資訊跟本0流通<br />\n<br />\n社會大眾對於塞鐵呢樣嘢最多係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">理解</span></span><br />\n但到底<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支唔支持</span></span>係未知之素<br />\n<br />\n而呢樣正正係雨革嘅死因 就係輿論同我地嘅評估有出入<br />\n<br />\n我預計自己應該會比人屌休息撚<br />\n不過以上係我自己塞咗3日鐵之後嘅評估黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請討論一下大家睇法"},{"pid":"681132068681b0dbcc4eaa27f97cbfd838458398","tid":1728684,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:39:06.000Z","msg":"Push!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1</a><br />\n深度分析，大家可以都睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d5ed692e7c40d8ef39caa039b191b421c0fff4","tid":1728684,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:42:21.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed5d8c45ac38853c6e2f70920b771e5f2a7b93d","tid":1728684,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:44:51.000Z","msg":"[長文]個人分析檢討有關依幾日感想 - 連續大型不合作運動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ewqcqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ewqcqS</a><br />\n<br />\nbut 我知前線唔接受依D Point, 因為人地真係抱住攬炒的心態去塞"},{"pid":"8ea108f779c4b74b2fc2d