bc3ea18","tid":1728684,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:01:40.000Z","msg":"「一成不變既模式」中文叫 慣性<br />\n<br />\n「一成不變的電視收看模式」中文叫 慣性收視"},{"pid":"14faf4dc477eaaf5d00da0bda24abb69193d6983","tid":1728684,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:03:05.000Z","msg":"我自己就已經唔會再睇連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6a78e7b597eb2871bfa885eac8be5a1861d6e1","tid":1728684,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14faf4dc477eaaf5d00da0bda24abb69193d6983","tid":1728684,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:03:05.000Z","msg":"我自己就已經唔會再睇連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:09:00.000Z","msg":"當然呢個都重要<br />\n但無可否認仲有好多人睇緊<br />\n甚至呢加先開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e77c90f40fe8617ec4159da23b1694d6f6854e","tid":1728684,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:16:58.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec41d737566daa566e8681bc426f1f119977b563","tid":1728684,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:17:32.000Z","msg":"<strong>他們在打的是「中共政權保衛戰」，而你們僅僅是在打「香港生活方式保衛戰」</strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，<strong>第一就是分化</strong>，<strong>把勇武派、和理非派拆分</strong>，<strong>第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」</strong>，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後<strong>隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"53bd5cf6f41d48e0eff591c6fa0dce899f38a640","tid":1728684,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf023e9fe97fe476c3cebcda7fcdeac80ef8c6f1","tid":1728684,"uid":76813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:31:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f57a0773ecc51a38f57a7d8a217f67c2b2913d54","tid":1728684,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44238dd5cedab5aaba36502f43ef1c637e797f0f","tid":1728684,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a48e704c7b3769d01a5f8c3324fbb8723592a60","tid":1728684,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:40:52.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5284da6a4357f57dc44f4a49f56acca7a578a1fe","tid":1728684,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:41:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d81e9e28fc861a5fea736a700c865d12b1ae8cff","tid":1728684,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204d043edc31acd1dc32b37a60fd610172560e